=== Operacao Lava Jato (Operation Car Wash) ===
==Political assassinations==
Brazil is one of the most dangerous countries for peasants, with sixty-five murders of peasants engaged in conflicts over the right to land in 2017 alone. Between 1985 and 2017, 1,722 activists of the Landless Movement were murdered.<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.bastamag.net/Le-Bresil-risque-de-subir-l-une-des-plus-grandes-regressions-ecologiques-et |title=Archived copy |access-date=2019-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730210840/https://www.bastamag.net/Le-Bresil-risque-de-subir-l-une-des-plus-grandes-regressions-ecologiques-et |archive-date=2017-07-30 |url-status=live }}</ref>
In 2016, at least 49 people were murdered in Brazil defending the environment against companies or landowners.<ref>http://www.geo.fr/environnement/au-moins-200-personnes-tuees-en-2016-pour-avoir-voulu-proteger-l-environnement-176677</ref>
